title: LIFE WILL HURT
itunes:title: LIFE WILL HURT
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
LIFE WILL HURT! Everyone gets knocked down in life. But how long will you stay down? No matter what you're going through you need to get up. Live and breathe and fight and believe and understand it is not over for you. Powerful new motivational speech and our latest release with Coach Pain (https://bit.ly/CoachPainMotiversity).


Music by Audiojungle (https://audiojungle.net/), and Paul Elhart (http://bit.ly/2SiEaIN).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
